examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_20/run2/fracture.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./d]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./bounds_dummy]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Bounds]
  [./nonnegtivity]
    type = BoundsAux
    variable = bounds_dummy
    bounded_variable = d
    upper = 1
    lower = 0
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./damage]
    type = PhaseFieldFractureEvolution
    variable = d
    driving_energy_name = E_el
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 8.333333E+01
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.973835E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.973835E+00'
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 2.511886E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 2.511886E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -snes_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'lu vinewtonrsls'
  dt = 6.835231E-06

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-06
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false

examples/mud_2D_qualitative/sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_seed_a/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_seed_a.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_sqexp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_seed_a.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

  [../]

    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'

  [../]

    velocity = vel_r
    beta = 0.25
    execute_on = timestep_end
  [../]
  [./vel_r]
    type = NewmarkVelAux
    variable = vel_r
    acceleration = accel_r
    gamma = 0.5
    execute_on = timestep_end
  [../]
  [./accel_z]
    type = NewmarkAccelAux
    variable = accel_z
    displacement = disp_z
    velocity = vel_z
    beta = 0.25
    execute_on = timestep_end
  [../]
  [./vel_z]
    type = NewmarkVelAux
    variable = vel_z
    acceleration = accel_z
    gamma = 0.5
    execute_on = timestep_end
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = RankTwoScalarAux
    variable = stress
    rank_two_tensor = stress
    scalar_type = MaxPrincipal
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./inertia_r]
    type = InertialForce
    variable = disp_r
    velocity = vel_r
    acceleration = accel_r
    beta = 0.25
    gamma = 0.5
  [../]
  [./inertia_z]
    type = InertialForce
    variable = disp_z
    velocity = vel_z
    acceleration = accel_z
    beta = 0.25
    gamma = 0.5
  [../]
  [./solid_r]
    type = ADStressDivergenceRZTensors
    variable = disp_r
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_r disp_z'
  [../]
  [./solid_z]
    type = ADStressDivergenceRZTensors
    variable = disp_z
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_r disp_z'
  [../]

  [./Hcond_time]
    type = ADHeatConductionTimeDerivative
    variable = T
  [../]
  [./Hcond]
    type = ADHeatConduction
    variable = T
  [../]
  [./Hsource]
    type = HeatSource
    variable = T
    function = 'if (t<1.000000E-06, 3.418703E+13*t, if (t<2.085000E-04, 3.418703E+07, if (t<2.095000E-04, 7.162184E+09-3.418703E+13*t, 0)))'
    block = source
  []
[]

[BCs]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = NEWTON
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels -snes_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                     vinewtonrsls'

  dt = 5e-9
  end_time = 2.095000E-04

  automatic_scaling = false
[]

[Outputs]
  file_base = run6
  print_linear_residuals = false
  exodus = true
  csv = true

  [../]

  [../]

  [../]

    block = 'film'
  [../]

examples/laser/run1/thermal_mechanical_dynamic.i

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = ../gold/geo2.msh
[]

[Problem]
  coord_type = RZ
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_r]
  [../]
  [./disp_z]
  [../]
  [./T]
    initial_condition = 300
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./vel_r]
  [../]
  [./vel_z]
  [../]
  [./accel_r]
  [../]
  [./accel_z]
  [../]
  [./stress]
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./bounds_dummy]
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
[]

[Postprocessors]
  [./thermal_ablation_volume]
    type = ThermalAblationVolume
    d = d
    temperature = T
    ablation_threshold = 1612
  [../]

  [./d_integral]
    type = ElementIntegralVariablePostprocessor
    variable = d
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Bounds]
  [./T]
    type = BoundsAux
    variable = bounds_dummy
    bounded_variable = T
    lower = 300
    execute_on = 'LINEAR TIMESTEP_BEGIN'
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc2.txt
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./density]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'density'
    prop_values = '2.0e-9'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    youngs_modulus = 2.74e4
    poissons_ratio = 0.25
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeAxisymmetricRZSmallStrain
    displacements = 'disp_r disp_z'
    eigenstrain_names = 'thermal_eigenstrain'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_StrainSpectral
    d = d
    history = false
  [../]

  [./thermal]
    type = HeatConductionMaterial
    temp = 'T'
    thermal_conductivity = 2.259
    specific_heat = 8.343e8
  [../]
  [./thermal_expansion]
    type = ADComputeThermalExpansionEigenstrain
    stress_free_temperature = '300'
    temperature = 'T'
    thermal_expansion_coeff = 8e-6
    eigenstrain_name = thermal_eigenstrain
  [../]

  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '0.0009'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = Gc
    L = 0.18
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./accel_r]
    type = NewmarkAccelAux
    variable = accel_r
    displacement = disp_r
    velocity = vel_r
    beta = 0.25
    execute_on = timestep_end
  [../]
  [./vel_r]
    type = NewmarkVelAux
    variable = vel_r
    acceleration = accel_r
    gamma = 0.5
    execute_on = timestep_end
  [../]
  [./accel_z]
    type = NewmarkAccelAux
    variable = accel_z
    displacement = disp_z
    velocity = vel_z
    beta = 0.25
    execute_on = timestep_end
  [../]
  [./vel_z]
    type = NewmarkVelAux
    variable = vel_z
    acceleration = accel_z
    gamma = 0.5
    execute_on = timestep_end
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = RankTwoScalarAux
    variable = stress
    rank_two_tensor = stress
    scalar_type = MaxPrincipal
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./inertia_r]
    type = InertialForce
    variable = disp_r
    velocity = vel_r
    acceleration = accel_r
    beta = 0.25
    gamma = 0.5
  [../]
  [./inertia_z]
    type = InertialForce
    variable = disp_z
    velocity = vel_z
    acceleration = accel_z
    beta = 0.25
    gamma = 0.5
  [../]
  [./solid_r]
    type = ADStressDivergenceRZTensors
    variable = disp_r
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_r disp_z'
  [../]
  [./solid_z]
    type = ADStressDivergenceRZTensors
    variable = disp_z
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_r disp_z'
  [../]

  [./Hcond_time]
    type = ADHeatConductionTimeDerivative
    variable = T
  [../]
  [./Hcond]
    type = ADHeatConduction
    variable = T
  [../]
  [./Hsource]
    type = HeatSource
    variable = T
    function = 'if (t<1.000000E-06, 1.891006E+13*t, if (t<1.000000E-04, 1.891006E+07, if (t<1.010000E-04, 1.909916E+09-1.891006E+13*t, 0)))'
    block = source
  []
[]

[BCs]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = NEWTON
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels -snes_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                     vinewtonrsls'

  dt = 5e-9
  end_time = 1.010000E-04

  automatic_scaling = false
[]

[Outputs]
  file_base = run1
  print_linear_residuals = false
  exodus = true
  csv = true
[]

    upper = 1
    lower = d_ref

    driving_energy_var = E_el

    prop_names = 'b'

    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

benchmarks/mode2_geometric_notch/fracture.i

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./d]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./bounds_dummy]
  [../]
[]

[Bounds]
  [./irreversibility]
    type = Irreversibility
    variable = 'bounds_dummy'
    bounded_variable = 'd'
    upper = 1
    lower = 'd_ref'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./react]
    type = PhaseFieldFractureEvolutionReaction
    variable = 'd'
    driving_energy_var = 'E_el'
  [../]
  [./diff]
    type = PhaseFieldFractureEvolutionDiffusion
    variable = 'd'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'energy_release_rate phase_field_regularization_length critical_fracture_energy'
    prop_values = '${Gc} ${l} ${psic}'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = ${k}
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -snes_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'lu vinewtonrsls'
  dt = 1e-6

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-08
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06
[]

[Outputs]
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./console]
    type = Console
    hide = 'load'
    outlier_variable_norms = false
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_2/run11/mechanical.i

    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]

    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture

    variable = 'disp_y'

    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture

  [../]

    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]

  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_200/run6/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./boundary_xdisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./boundary_ydisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./Periodic]
    [./disp_x]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '3.981072E+00 0 0'
    [../]
    [./disp_y]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '3.981072E+00 0 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 8.333333E+02
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.973835E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.973835E+00'
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 3.981072E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 3.981072E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Postprocessors]
  [./fracture_energy]
    type = FractureEnergy
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = TransientSupNorm
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  dt = 5.981584E-06

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load fracture_energy'
  exodus = true
  print_linear_residuals = false
[]
Close

    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'

    coefficient = 0.1

      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'

    [../]

      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]

      primary = 'top'

    [../]

  [../]

    value = 0

  [../]

    initial_stress_yy = load

  [../]

    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]

    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz

    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'

  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]

    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

    value = 0
  [../]

      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '5.011872E+00 0 0'
    [../]
    [./disp_y]

      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '5.011872E+00 0 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Materials]

    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 8.333333E+01
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.973835E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '3.973835E+00'
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 5.011872E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 5.011872E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
  [../]

    d = d
  [../]

    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./get_E_el]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
  [../]
  [./send_load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
  [../]
  [./send_d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./d]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./bounds_dummy]
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./left_right]
      variable = d
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./top_bottom]
      variable = d
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Bounds]
  [./irreversibility]
    type = Irreversibility
    variable = bounds_dummy
    bounded_variable = d
    upper = 1
    lower = d_ref
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./damage]
    type = PhaseFieldFractureEvolution
    variable = d
    driving_energy_var = E_el
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = StationaryGenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = TransientSupNorm
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -snes_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'lu vinewtonrsls'

  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06
[]

  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false

    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./boundary_xdisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./boundary_ydisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./Periodic]
    [./disp_x]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '3.162278E+01 0 0'
    [../]
    [./disp_y]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '3.162278E+01 0 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+01
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '5.812010E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '5.812010E+00'
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 3.162278E-01
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 3.162278E-01
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Postprocessors]
  [./fracture_energy]
    type = FractureEnergy
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = TransientSupNorm
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  dt = 4.921048E-06

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load fracture_energy'
  exodus = true
  print_linear_residuals = false
[]
Close

examples/mud_2D/gold/fracture.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = %s
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = %s
  [../]
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./mechanical]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'mechanical.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./get_E_el]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
  [../]
  [./send_load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
  [../]
  [./send_d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./d]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./bounds_dummy]
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./left_right]
      variable = d
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./top_bottom]
      variable = d
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Bounds]
  [./irreversibility]
    type = Irreversibility
    variable = bounds_dummy
    bounded_variable = d
    upper = 1
    lower = d_ref
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./damage]
    type = PhaseFieldFractureEvolution
    variable = d
    driving_energy_var = E_el
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = StationaryGenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = TransientSupNorm
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -snes_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'lu vinewtonrsls'
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-06
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
[]
Close

    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'

      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]

      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]

  [../]

    value = 0

  [../]

    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]

    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

  [../]

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]

    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'

  [../]

examples/mud_3D/L_6/fracture.i

[Functions]
  [./psic]

  [../]

    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = '../gold/Gc_L_6_rho_0_sample_1.txt'
  [../]
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./mechanical]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'mechanical.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./get_E_el]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
  [../]
  [./send_load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
  [../]
  [./send_d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./d]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./bounds_dummy]
  [../]
[]

[Bounds]
  [./irreversibility]
    type = Irreversibility
    variable = bounds_dummy
    bounded_variable = d
    upper = 1
    lower = d_ref
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./damage]
    type = PhaseFieldFractureEvolution
    variable = d
    driving_energy_var = E_el
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = StationaryGenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = TransientSupNorm
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -snes_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'lu vinewtonrsls'
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-06
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06
[]

  hide = 'load'

examples/mud_2D/exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0.5_sample_6/mechanical.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0.5_sample_6.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0.5_sample_6.txt
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
  [./strain_zz]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

  [../]

    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]

    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]

      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]

      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]

    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]

    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]

    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d

    history = false
  [../]

  [../]

  [../]

    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3

  [../]

  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]

    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

  [../]

    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    variable = disp_x

    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]

      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]

      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_2D/exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_5/fracture.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/Gc_exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_5.txt
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = ../gold/psic_exp_cartesian_5_5_rho_0_sample_5.txt
  [../]
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./mechanical]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'mechanical.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./get_E_el]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
  [../]
  [./send_load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
  [../]
  [./send_d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./d]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./bounds_dummy]
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./left_right]
      variable = d
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./top_bottom]
      variable = d
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Bounds]
  [./irreversibility]
    type = Irreversibility
    variable = bounds_dummy
    bounded_variable = d
    upper = 1
    lower = d_ref
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./damage]
    type = PhaseFieldFractureEvolution
    variable = d
    driving_energy_var = E_el
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = StationaryGenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = TransientSupNorm
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -snes_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'lu vinewtonrsls'
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-06
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
[]
Close

  [./Gc]
  [../]
  [./psic]
  [../]
[]

[AuxKernels]
  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
  [./Gc]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = Gc
    function = Gc
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = FunctionAux
    variable = psic
    function = psic
    execute_on = 'INITIAL'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./plane_stress]
    type = ADWeakPlaneStress
    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./react_x]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]
    type = DegradedCoefReaction
    variable = disp_y
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./x_left_right]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
  [./x_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

  [../]

    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    variable = strain_zz
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    variable = disp_x
    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]
  [./react_y]

    coefficient = 0.1
  [../]

      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./y_left_right]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./x_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
    [./y_top_bottom]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]

    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]

    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]

  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]
Close

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_1/run1/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./boundary_xdisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./boundary_ydisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./Periodic]
    [./disp_x]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '2.511886E+00 0 0'
    [../]
    [./disp_y]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '2.511886E+00 0 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '4.048456E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '4.048456E+00'
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 2.511886E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 2.511886E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Postprocessors]
  [./fracture_energy]
    type = FractureEnergy
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = TransientSupNorm
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type'
  petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  dt = 7.909280E-06

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  exodus = true
  print_linear_residuals = false

examples/mud_quasi1D_analytical/script_varying_L_Eratio_5/run4/mechanical.i

[GlobalParams]
  displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'geo.msh'
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./fracture]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./disp_x]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_x'
    variable = 'disp_x'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'disp_y'
    variable = 'disp_y'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
  [./load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
    execute_on = SAME_AS_MULTIAPP
  [../]
[]

[Variables]
  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./d]
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_x
    component = 0
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = disp_y
    component = 1
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./boundary_xdisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./boundary_ydisp]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_y
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./Periodic]
    [./disp_x]
      variable = disp_x
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '5.011872E+00 0 0'
    [../]
    [./disp_y]
      variable = disp_y
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '5.011872E+00 0 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./eigen_strain]
    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_film]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 4.166667E+00
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./elasticity_tensor_substrate]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 2.000000E-01
    youngs_modulus = 2.083333E+01
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    eigenstrain_names = is
  [../]
  [./stress_film]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    history = false
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./stress_substrate]
    type = SmallStrainPK2Stress
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_film]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '5.503124E-04'
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier_substrate]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '5.503124E+00'
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_film]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 5.011872E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties_substrate]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 8.000000E-04
    L = 5.011872E-02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'substrate'
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
  [../]
[]

[Postprocessors]
  [./fracture_energy]
    type = FractureEnergy
    d = d
  [../]
[]

  type = TransientSupNorm
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'

  petsc_options_value = 'lu'

  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  exodus = true

  [../]

    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp

    variable = 'disp_y'

    variable = 'd_ref'

    direction = from_multiapp

    variable = 'd'

benchmarks/mode2_geometric_notch/mechanical.i

[MultiApps]

    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'fracture.i'

    cli_args = 'Gc=${Gc};l=${l};psic=${psic};k=${k}'

  [./send_E_el]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
  [../]
  [./send_d_ref]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd_ref'
    variable = 'd_ref'
  [../]
  [./get_d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = fracture
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = 'gold/geo.msh'
[]

  [./disp_x]
  [../]
  [./disp_y]
  [../]

  [../]

    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL

  [../]

  [./E_el]
    type = MaterialRealAux
    property = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./solid_x]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = 'disp_x'
    component = 0
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
    save_in = 'fx'
  [../]
  [./solid_y]
    type = ADStressDivergenceTensors
    variable = 'disp_y'
    component = 1
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./xdisp]
    type = ScalarDirichletBC
    variable = 'disp_x'
    boundary = 'top'
    scalar_var = 'load'
  [../]
  [./yfix]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = 'disp_y'
    boundary = 'top bottom left right'
    value = 0
  [../]
  [./xfix]
    type = DirichletBC
    variable = 'disp_x'
    boundary = 'bottom'
    value = 0
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./elasticity_tensor]
    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    youngs_modulus = ${E}
    poissons_ratio = ${nu}
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputeSmallStrain
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]
  [./stress]
    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_StrainSpectral
    d = 'd'
    d_crit = ${dc}
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'energy_release_rate phase_field_regularization_length critical_fracture_energy'
    prop_values = '${Gc} ${l} ${psic}'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./phase_field_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = ${k}
  [../]
[]

[Executioner]
  type = TransientSubcycling
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -pc_factor_mat_solver_package'
  petsc_options_value = 'lu       superlu_dist'
  # petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  # petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          1000        200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-6

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-08
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
  compute_scaling_once = false
[]

[Postprocessors]
  [./Fx]
    type = NodalSum
    variable = 'fx'
    boundary = 'top'
  [../]
[]

[Outputs]
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./csv]
    type = CSV
    delimiter = ' '
    file_base = 'force_displacement'
    time_column = false
  [../]
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    file_base = 'visualize'

    hide = 'load Fx'
  [../]

  [./strain]

    eigenstrain_names = is

  [../]

  [../]

    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
    block = 'film'
  [../]

    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'

  [../]

    function = 't'
  [../]

    variable = disp_y
    boundary = 1
    value = 0
  [../]

    variable = disp_x

    value = 0
  [../]
[]

    C_ijkl = '120.0 80.0'
    fill_method = symmetric_isotropic

  [./strain]

    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    type = SmallStrainDegradedPK2Stress_NoSplit
    d = d
    # d_crit = 0.95
    # history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = GenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = '0.005'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 1e-3
    L = 0.02
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]
  [./degradation]
    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06

    # lag_degradation = true
  [../]

examples/mud_2D_sensitivity/Gc_constant_rho_1/fracture.i

[Functions]
  [./Gc]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = '../gold/Gc_sqexp_Gc_constant_rho_1_sample_1.txt'
  [../]
  [./psic]
    type = PiecewiseMultilinear
    data_file = '../gold/psic_sqexp_Gc_constant_rho_1_sample_1.txt'
  [../]
[]

[MultiApps]
  [./mechanical]
    type = TransientMultiApp
    input_files = 'mechanical.i'
    app_type = raccoonApp
    execute_on = 'TIMESTEP_END'
  [../]
[]

[Transfers]
  [./get_E_el]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = from_multiapp
    source_variable = 'E_el'
    variable = 'E_el'
  [../]
  [./send_load]
    type = MultiAppScalarToAuxScalarTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'load'
    to_aux_scalar = 'load'
  [../]
  [./send_d]
    type = MultiAppCopyTransfer
    multi_app = mechanical
    direction = to_multiapp
    source_variable = 'd'
    variable = 'd'
  [../]
[]

[Mesh]
  type = FileMesh
  file = '../gold/geo.msh'
[]

[Variables]
  [./d]
  [../]
[]

[AuxVariables]
  [./load]
    family = SCALAR
  [../]
  [./E_el]
    order = CONSTANT
    family = MONOMIAL
  [../]
  [./d_ref]
  [../]
  [./bounds_dummy]
  [../]
[]

[BCs]
  [./Periodic]
    [./left_right]
      variable = d
      primary = 'left'
      secondary = 'right'
      translation = '100 0 0'
    [../]
    [./top_bottom]
      variable = d
      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]
  [../]
[]

[Bounds]
  [./irreversibility]
    type = Irreversibility
    variable = bounds_dummy
    bounded_variable = d
    upper = 1
    lower = d_ref
  [../]
[]

[Kernels]
  [./react]
    type = PhaseFieldFractureEvolutionReaction
    variable = d
    driving_energy_var = E_el
  [../]
  [./diff]
    type = PhaseFieldFractureEvolutionDiffusion
    variable = d
    driving_energy_var = E_el
  [../]
[]

[Materials]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]
    type = StationaryGenericFunctionMaterial
    prop_names = 'energy_release_rate b'
    prop_values = 'Gc psic'
  [../]
  [./length_scale]
    type = GenericConstantMaterial
    prop_names = 'phase_field_regularization_length'

    [../]

      primary = 'top'
      secondary = 'bottom'

    [../]

      secondary = 'bottom'
      translation = '0 -100 0'
    [../]

    type = DirichletBC
    variable = disp_x
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center'
  [../]
  [./y_pin]

    variable = disp_y
    value = 0
    boundary = 'center pin'
  [../]

    type = ComputeEigenstrainFromScalarInitialStress
    initial_stress_xx = load
    initial_stress_yy = load
    eigenstrain_name = is
  [../]

    type = ComputeIsotropicElasticityTensor
    poissons_ratio = 0.2
    youngs_modulus = 4
  [../]
  [./strain]
    type = ADComputePlaneSmallStrain
    out_of_plane_strain = strain_zz
    eigenstrain_names = is
    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
  [../]

    d = d
    d_crit = 0.6
    history = false
  [../]
  [./fracture_energy_barrier]

    prop_names = 'b'
    prop_values = 'psic'
  [../]
  [./local_dissipation]
    type = LinearLocalDissipation
    d = d
  [../]
  [./fracture_properties]
    type = FractureMaterial
    Gc = 'Gc'
    L = 0.5
    local_dissipation_norm = 8/3
  [../]

    type = LorentzDegradation
    d = d
    residual_degradation = 1e-06
  [../]
[]

  type = Transient
  solve_type = 'NEWTON'

  # petsc_options_value = 'lu'
  petsc_options_iname = '-pc_type -sub_pc_type -ksp_max_it -ksp_gmres_restart -sub_pc_factor_levels'
  petsc_options_value = 'asm      ilu          200         200                0                    '
  dt = 1e-4

  nl_abs_tol = 1e-10
  nl_rel_tol = 1e-06

  automatic_scaling = true
[]

[Outputs]
  hide = 'load'
  print_linear_residuals = false
  [./exodus]
    type = Exodus
    execute_on = 'FINAL'
  [../]
[]

    displacements = 'disp_x disp_y'
